column1: #Text=But we do n't think about it right now because now we are really excited about the new album coming out .
#Text=I could see it go many ways .
#Text=I have a difficult time seeing myself touring when I 'm 55 years old ; I probably would n't want to do that .
#Text=Not the way I do it now , at least .
#Text=Yeah , it is difficult to see myself as a grandmother on stage .
#Text=Are there venues that you guys have n't played that is your dream venue ?
#Text=I always really , really want to play that as a headliner .
#Text=That would be really great , I think .
#Text=The Hollywood Bowl would be really amazing .

#Text=And we were lucky enough to play the Wembley Arena once , but the only thing that happened was they put us on the program at the wrong time , so we actually had to go on before the doors even opened !
#Text=We actually ended up playing for four people in this big arena : our producer , his wife and a few of our friends .
#Text=It was really cool ; we enjoyed it .
#Text=And then halfway through the set they actually opened the doors and people started coming in so in the end we maybe played for a few thousand .
#Text=It was like a dream come true .
#Text=We always wanted to play Wembley Arena !
#Text=It was a really good show , actually .
#Text=Yeah , like Sune was saying , Madison Square Garden would definitely be something very ...
#Text=If Jay-Z can do it , we can too !
#Text=Are there any bands you guys would love to play with ?
#Text=I always wanted to tour with Primal Scream .
#Text=I would like to open for Bob Dylan , but I would be a little scared of meeting him , I think .
#Text=Dont Look Back - have you seen that ?
#Text=Are you more worried about him being intimidating or disappointing ?
#Text=I would worry about him being disappointing .
#Text=I would worry about him being -- which I have heard that he is -- pretty grumpy ; mean .
#Text=Do you believe in a higher power ?
#Text=I do sort of believe in a higher power in a very scientific way ; I believe in the fourth dimension and time travel ...
